---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-ink/10 py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-stone md:flex-row">
      <span>&copy; {year} Signal Advisory LLC. Kansas City, Missouri.</span>
      <span>Independent. Carrier agnostic. On your side of the table.</span>
    </div>

    <!-- FCC commission disclosure. Required-style language for channel advisors
         that earn carrier commissions. Have counsel review before launch. -->
    <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xs leading-relaxed text-stone/80">
      <strong class="font-semibold text-stone">Compensation disclosure:</strong>
      Signal Advisory LLC is an authorized agent for various telecommunications and
      technology service providers and may receive commissions or referral fees on
      services purchased through our recommendations. Our advisory and sourcing
      engagements remain client-aligned: we represent the interests of our clients
      in carrier evaluation, contract negotiation, and account management. Specific
      compensation arrangements are disclosed on request.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
